      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Black_White_1.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/625672304/RenderMan_Black_White_1.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1760445299870&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=387\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/625672304/RenderMan_Black_White_1.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1760445299870&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"980\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"625672311\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Black_White_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"625672304\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"8\" data-media-id=\"bba5efb1-e5f1-4116-bde6-a0f9ea0a04b8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/625672304/RenderMan_Black_White_1.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1760445299870&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=774 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/625672304/RenderMan_Black_White_1.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1760445299870&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=387 1x\"></span><p>Everyone knows what Black and White colors mean in rendering, right?</p><p>Of course!</p><p>Well …. just in case, here’s a quick guide on how RenderMan treats Black and White values when it comes to Roughness, Metallic, and Bump.</p><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"0c0e3fc0-6477-4cbe-ab93-e34b48ac2722\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Material Roughness</span></strong></p>\n</div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong>Black = Shiny</strong></p><p>Roughness Value: 1</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong>White = Rough</strong></p><p>Roughness Value: 0</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"9e92ef94-7e4e-45a5-bc63-86954d9afbf5\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Material Metallic Workflow</span></strong></p>\n</div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong>Black = Non-Metal</strong></p><p>Roughness Value: 1</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong>White = Metal</strong></p><p>Roughness Value: 0</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"e5167639-406f-4d1a-9ab2-9b08c9cd77b1\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Bump Maps</span></strong></p>\n</div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong>Black = Bump In</strong></p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong>White = Bump Out</strong></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"8ee88b30-dcfb-410e-b27b-8462d5c0c36b\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Displacement Maps</span></strong></p>\n</div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong>Black = Displace Inwards</strong></p><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong>White = Displace Outwards</strong></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"93be057c-86d4-42fa-bb70-5621572c8950\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Presence (Opacity)</span></strong></p>\n</div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong>Black = OFF</strong></p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong>White = ON</strong></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
